15/09/2009
BRUSSELS, Belgium -- Turkish Cypriot leader Mehmet Ali Talat met for an hour in Brussels on Monday (September 14th) with EU Enlargement Commissioner Olli Rehn. Talat, who recently resumed reunification talks regarding the divided island, said afterwards that he does not want the bloc to press the Greek Cypriot administration; rather, the EU should motivate them, he said. (Anadolu news agency, ABHaber, CNN Turk - 14/09/09)
